{"tid":2009711,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"【瘋搶公屋】彩霞邨臨場反價10萬 綠表賣430萬貴絕觀塘","createTime":"2020-05-10T03:10:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T06:06:07.000Z","uid":301508,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"6621ba4ed3e93e9e4779de6a720ab5d101d04ae0","tid":2009711,"uid":301508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"隨着香港疫情緩和，樓市氣氛好轉，買家重現癲價搶盤。近期資助房屋連環錄高價成交，九龍灣公屋彩霞邨一個三房單位，新近以綠表價430萬元易手，成為觀塘歷來最貴未補地價公屋。<br />\n<br />\n富誠地產何庭欣表示，新公屋王為彩霞邨A座中層10室，單位為3房間隔，實用面積598方呎，座向東北望公園景，單位今年3月底放售，綠表叫價420萬元，放盤5天超過20組客睇樓，當中三組客出價洽購。業主與家人商議後，決定加價10萬元，隨即一名準買家零還價以430萬元購入，呎價7,191元。代理稱，彩霞邨位於九龍灣位置，步行至港鐵站約5至8分鐘。該區配套完善，交通四通八達，加上按揭成數高，供款年期長，故此大受歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n原業主2010年8月以78.8萬元綠表購入，持有單位10年，是次轉手賬面獲利351.2萬元，升值4.5倍。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200505/MHJAXN4457DT26GWNQ6SKU7OEQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200505%2FMHJAXN4457DT26GWNQ6SKU7OEQ%2F&d=EEWyN02WlTtsLATURr%2FfpZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=8aea4dab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200505%2FMHJAXN4457DT26GWNQ6SKU7OEQ%2F&h=c152541b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200505/MHJAXN4457DT26GWNQ6SKU7OEQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n租置戶WIN WIN <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e18244486a798d8d925d562082b8bcb14453a3c2","tid":2009711,"uid":135957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:14:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a052cf88226fea53b77465f85459a024805ed063","tid":2009711,"uid":16955,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"e18244486a798d8d925d562082b8bcb14453a3c2","tid":2009711,"uid":135957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:14:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T03:26:34.000Z","msg":"買個個正on9<br />\n打死唔會買租置公屋"},{"pid":"ba798f824b9240e2ced0eb12801c56889482104c","tid":2009711,"uid":239912,"like":